These Tie Dye Side Super Skinny Jeans have a 5 pocket design with one coin pocket on the front and two pockets on the back. The jeans are then rounded off with thy brands famous 'Maison Scotch' leather tab on the back waistband.

Barbour Steve McQueen Casual Thunder Jacket100% CottonLong SleevesFull Front Zip and Press Stud Fastening5 Press Stud Fastened PocketsDuring the East German 1964 International Six Day Trials in which Steve McQueen competed, he was never seen without his Barbour International motorcycle jacket. So much so that the US team followed suit and each bought their own to protect themselves from the harsh weather. Now in the jacket?s 75th anniversary Barbour has produced this collection to honour both the jacket and the star who wore it. Combine this with their Barbour Kids range and you have new and exciting garments for your little ones too. This Casual Thunder Jacket has been designed with long sleeves and a crew neck line. The collar has a press stud fastening which can be folded back on itself and secured using a different press stud when not in use. the inside of the collar has been designed using a cord fabric so looks great folded down or up. It has a full front zip fastening with concealed press studs running down for extra security and a clean over all finish. The jacket has then been designed with 4 single welt press stud pockets on the inside and one press stud pocket on the inside. The jacket has been given an adjustable, drawstring waist which is secured just behind the zip on each side using press studs. It has been given a soft cotton lining for extra comfort and has numerous design features including appliqued material patches, soldier shoulder epaulettes and the renowned designer Barbour branding embroidered onto the welt of the left side bottom pocket.
